  </div>");
			Add("hr", "FriendlyContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
[Friendly] je meč na [GameBoard] kojega možete voditi samo za zabavu i vježbu. Možete izabrati [Fleet] bitke i vašeg protivnika. Ove bitke se ne uzimaju u obzir za vaš [ELO].
<p />
Možete se koristiti ovim bitkama da provate nove [BattleTactics], da bolje upoznate neke [CombatUnits] ili da vježbate za [Tournaments].
</div>");
			Add("pt", "FriendlyContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Os [Friendly] são combates no [GameBoard] que podes fazer só por divertimento ou para praticar. Podes escolher a [Fleet] da batalha e o teu oponente.
    Estas batalhas não são tidas em conta para a tua [ELO].
    <p />
    Podes usar estas batalhas para testar novas [BattleTactics], conhecer melhor algumas [CombatUnits] ou para praticar para [Tournaments].
  </div>");
			Add("de", "GameBoardContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Das [GameBoard] ist Ort wo die Kämpfe stattfinden. 
    <p>
    Die gängigste Form der Schlacht, die 1 gegen 1, hat das Spielbrett 8 Vierecke Höhe mal 8 Vierecke
    Breite die eine Summe von 64 Vierecken ergibt (genauso wie ein Schachbrett). 
    </p><p><img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/GameBoard2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"1 vs 1 Game Board" + '"' + @" /></p><p>
    In der 2 gegen 2 Schalcht, hat das Spielbrett 12 Vierecke Höhe mal 12 Vierecke Breite mit einem 
    kleinen Detail: an jeder Ecke, sind vier Vierecke die der Spieler nicht benutzen kann. 
    Deshalb sind nur 128 Vierecke verfügbar.
    <img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/GameBoard4.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"2 vs 2 Game Board" + '"' + @" /></p></div>");
			Add("en", "GameBoardContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    The [GameBoard] is the area where the battle is made. 
    <p />
    In the most common form of battle, the 1 vs 1, the game board has 8 squares heigh by 8 squares width performing a total of 64 squares (just like a chess board). 
    <p /><img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/GameBoard2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"1 vs 1 Game Board" + '"' + @" /><p />
    In the 2 vs 2 battle, the game board has 12 squares heigth by 12 squares width with a small detail: in each corner, there are 4 squares that are not player cannot use. 
    Because of that there only are 128 available squares.
    <img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/GameBoard4.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"2 vs 2 Game Board" + '"' + @" /></div>");
			Add("es", "GameBoardContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    El [GameBoard] es el area donde se hacen las batallas.
    <p />
    La forma mas común de batalla, el 1 vs 1, el tablero de juego tiene 8 cuadriculas de largo por 8 cuadriculas de ancho con un total de 64 cuadrados posibles (tal como un  tablero de ajedrez).
    <p /><img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/GameBoard2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Tabuleiro 1 vs 1" + '"' + @" /><p />
    En la formar 2 vs 2, el tablero tiene 12 cuadrados de largo por 12 cuadrados de ancho con un pequeño detalle: En las esquinas existen 4 cuadrados que el jugador no puede  usar. Por eso tiene 128 cuadrados de juego.
    <img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/GameBoard4.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Tabuleiro 2 vs 2" + '"' + @" /></div>");
			Add("fr", "GameBoardContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Le [GameBoard] est l’endroit où les combats ont lieu.    <p />
    Dans la forme de bataille la plus commune, 1 vs 1, le plateau de jeu a une longueur et largeur de 8 (8X) totalisant 64 cases, comme aux échecs. 
    <p /><img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/GameBoard2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"1 vs 1 Game Board" + '"' + @" /><p />
    Dans les combats 2 vs. 2, le plateau de jeu possède 12 cases en longueur et largeur, mais 4 cases dans chaque coin ne peuvent être utilisés par les joueurs. Il y a donc 128 cases de disponibles.
    <img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/GameBoard4.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"2 vs 2 Game Board" + '"' + @" /></div>");
			Add("hr", "GameBoardContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
