  </p></div>");
			Add("en", "RelicsContent", @"<h1>Relics</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    A [Relic] is a special body on the [Universe], specially designed for [Alliance] wars. When an [Alliance] has one or more [Relics],
    all alliance members will receive a rare resource per day. The income per player depends on how many relics the [Alliance] holds
    and his/her alliance rank.
    <p />
    The total income that the [Alliance] will receive is given by the following data:
    <ul><li>Each relic will contribute with K multiplied by it's [ZoneLevel]; if the relic is at war, the income will be decreased up to eight times</li><li>The sum of the income from all relics is then multiplied by the percentage of relics on the universe that the alliance holds</li></ul>
    This means that more [Relics] will give even more resources. K is an internal constant, subject to change. 
    <p />
    Each [Relic] has its own protector: an alliance member that conquers the relic and then is responsible for defending it.
  </div>");
			Add("fr", "RelicsContent", @"<h1>Reliques</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
