    <ul><li>[BuyIntrinsicDeduction]</li><li>[BuyRareDeduction]</li><li>[BuyQueueSpace]</li><li>[BuyFastSpeed]</li><li>[BuyFullLineOfSight]</li><li>[BuyNoUndiscoveredUniverse]</li></ul><a name=" + '"' + @"BuyIntrinsicDeduction" + '"' + @" id=" + '"' + @"BuyIntrinsicDeduction" + '"' + @"></a><h2>[BuyIntrinsicDeduction]</h2>
