    Unlike the previous service, this is only valid for rare resources: [Astatine], [Prismal], [Radon], [Cryptium]
    and [Argon].

    <a name=" + '"' + @"BuyQueueSpace" + '"' + @" id=" + '"' + @"BuyQueueSpace" + '"' + @"></a><h2>[BuyQueueSpace]</h2>
    The queue space is the amount of [Facilities] or [CombatUnits] that you are able to put on hold for
