    Feuerkraft.

  </div>");
			Add("en", "LightHumansUnitsContent", @"<h2>Combat Units</h2><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    [LightHumans] have [CombatUnits] more prepared for defense than for fire power.

  </div>");
			Add("es", "LightHumansUnitsContent", @"<h2>Unidades de Combate</h2><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Los [LightHumans] tienen [CombatUnits] mas preparadas para defender que para atacar. 
