			Add("de", "AcademyManual", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/Academy.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"float: right;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Akademie" + '"' + @" />
    Akademie ist ein Universum Gebäube das 2 Zwecken dient:
    <ul><li>Als erstes den Spielern zu helfen die Kopfgeldjäger sind, die Piraten aufzuspüren.</li><li>Als zweites Mission zu liefern die nur mit gewissen Fraktionen zu tun haben. Zum Beispiel Metallic Beard Missionen werden in der Akademie abgeliefert.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("en", "AcademyManual", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/Academy.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"float:right;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Academy" + '"' + @" />
    Academy is a universe building that serves 2 Proposes:
    <ul><li>The first is to help players that have the Bounty Hunter profession to track Pirates.</li><li>The second is to deliver quests that are relacted to certain factions. For instance Metallic Beard's quests are delivered at the Academy.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("hr", "AcademyManual", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/Academy.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"float:right;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Academy" + '"' + @" />
Akademija je svemirska zgrada koja služi za dvije Svrhe:
<ul><li>Prva je da pomogne igračima koji imaju profesije Lovca na Glave da prate Pirate. </li><li> Druga je da dostavi misije koje su povezane sa određenim fakcijama. Na primjer zadatak Metalne Brade se dostavlja u Akademiju.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("pt", "AcademyManual", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/Academy.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"float:right;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Academy" + '"' + @" />
    A Academia é um edificio no universo que serve 2 propósitos:
    <ul><li>O primeiro é ajudar os jogadores que têm a profissão de Caçadores de prémios a procurar Piratas.</li><li>O segundo é servirem como ponto de entrega de missões que estão relacionadas com certas facções. Por exemplo, as missões relativas ao Barba Metálica são entregues nas Academias.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("de", "ArenaManual", @"Die [Arena] ist der Platz der Wahl für kriegerische Spieler, wo es eine Chance gibt für Ruhm und Ehre 
  zu kämpfen. <p>
  Es gibt unzählige [Arenas] im ganzen [Universe], wobei je näher es zum Zentrum des [Universe] ist umso grösser ist die Belohnung für den Sieg. </p><p>
  Wenn ein Spieler eine leere [Arena] findet wird er automatisch zum Champion dieser [Arena], andernfalls kann er den gegenwärtigen Champion herausfordern, und die [Flotte] der Schlacht wird eine [Flotte] sein die nicht vor irgendeinem der Spieler ausgewählt wird, sondern eine [Flotte] die gleich für beide Spieler ist und die von der [Arena] für eine Schlacht zur Verfügung gestellt wird. Im Falle des Siegs wird der Champion ungekrönt und
  der neue Champion wird für diese [Arena] gekrönt. </p><p>
  Aber der grösste Ansporn ist die Möglichkeit [Orions] zu gewinnen. Der Herausforderer muss [Orions] bezahlen um den Champion herauszufordern, und wenn der Champion die Schlacht gewinnt, dann gewinnt er auch einen Teil der [Orions] die von dem Herausforderer bezahlt wurde. Je mehr [Arena] Schlachten der Spieler gewinnt umso mehr Punkte verdient er für den Beruf des [Gladiator].
Die einzige Frage ist - <i>Mit wievielen [Arenas] kannst du fertigwerden als Champion?</i></p>");
			Add("en", "ArenaManual", @"The [Arena] is the place of choice for warrior players, where there is a chance to fight for glory and prestige. <p />
  There are several [Arenas] along in the [Universe], whereas the more to the center of [Universe] the greater is the reward for victory. <p />
  When a player find an empty [Arena] he becomes automatically the champion of that [Arena], otherwise he may challenge
  the current champion, and the [Fleet] of the battle will be a [Fleet] that is not chosen by any of the players, but will be a [Fleet] equal
  for both players made available by the [Arena] just for one battle. In case of victory the champion is uncrowned and
  a new champion is crowned for that [Arena]. <p />
  But the biggest incentive is the possibility of winning [Orions]. The challenger has to pay [Orions] to challenge the champion, if
  the champion wins the battle, he also wins part of the [Orions] paid by the challenger. The more [Arena] battles a player win more points 
  he wins for the profession of [Gladiator].
  The only question is - <i>How many [Arenas] can you handle as champion?</i>");
			Add("hr", "ArenaManual", @"[Arena] je mjesto izbora za ratničke igrače, gdje imate šansu da se borite za slavu i prestiž.<p />
Postoji nekoliko [Arenas] s kraja na kraj [Universe], što su bliže centru [Universe] to je veća nagrada za pobjedu.  <p />
Kada igrač pronađe praznu [Arena] automatski postaje prvak te [Arena], ili pak mora izazvati trenutačnog prvaka, i [Fleet] bitke neće biti [Fleet] koja je izabrana od jednog od igrača, već će biti jednaka [Fleet] za oba igrača koja je dostupna od strane [Arena] samo za jednu bitku. U slučaju pobjede prvak je skinut sa trona i novi prvak je okunjen za tu [Arena]. <p />
Ali najveća motivacija je mogućnost da se dobiju [Orions]. Izazivač mora platiti [Orions] da izazove prvaka, ako prvak dobije bitku, on također dobija dio [Orions] plaćenih od strane izazivača. Što više bitaka [Arena] igrač odigra to dobija više bodova za profesiju [Gladiator].
Jedino pitanje je - <i>Koliko [Arenas] možete držati kao prvak?</i>");
			Add("pt", "ArenaManual", @"A [Arena] é o local de eleição dos jogadores guerreiros, onde há a oportunidade de lutar pelo reconhecimento e prestígio.<p />
  Existem diversas [Arenas] pelo [Universe], sendo que quanto mais para o centro do [Universe] se for maior é a recompensa pela vitória.<p />
  Quando um jogador encontra uma [Arena] desocupada passa automaticamente a ser o campeão dessa [Arena], caso contrário pode desafiar 
  o campeão actual, sendo que a [Fleet] da batalha irá ser uma [Fleet] não escolhida por nenhum dos jogadores, mas sim uma [Fleet] igual 
  para os dois jogadores que é disponibilizada pela [Arena] só para a batalha em questão. No caso de vitória o campeão é destronado e 
  é coroado um novo campeão daquela [Arena].<p />
  Mas o maior incentivo é a possibilidade de ganhar [Orions]. O jogador que desafia o campeão tem de pagar [Orions] para o desafiar, no caso
  do campeão ganhar, ganha também parte dos [Orions] pagos pelo oponente. Quanto mais batalhas de [Arena] se ganhar mais pontos se 
  ganha na profissão de [Gladiator]. A pergunta é só - <i>De quantas [Arenas] consegues ser campeão?</i>");
			Add("en", "BeaconContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/BeaconImg.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"float:right;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Beacon" + '"' + @" /><p>The [Beacon] it's the [LightHumans] Ultimate Weapon. Like the name suggests, it's something that is going to patrol a certain region of the universe. And it's exactly that.</p><p>When you place a [Beacon] it will, depending on its level, give information of the surrounding [Planet]s and [Fleet]s. It also prevents [Devastation]s to the fired in the area covered by the [Beacon].</p><p>Its level is given by the sum of the levels of your [DeepSpaceScanner]. Example: if you have 3 [DeepSpaceScanner] level 1 and 1 [DeepSpaceScanner] level 2, then your [Beacon] level will be 5.</p><h2>How to Create</h2><p>A Beacon can be created by any fleet. If all conditions are met (necessary resources and, depending of the level, if you're near a planet that you own), the folowing option will appear in the
    fleet popup:</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/BeaconUsage.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"float:right;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Beacon" + '"' + @" /><h1>States</h1>
