  The [DeepSpaceScanner] is not built in any of your private planets.
 </li><li><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/BeaconNotReady.gif" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Beacon Not Ready" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Beacon Not Ready" + '"' + @" /><br />
