			Add("de", "FleetContent", @"<h1>Fleets</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
   Die [Flotte] ist eine Gruppe von [CombatUnits] die [Travel](reisen) können im [Universe]. Es gibt 
    verschieden Arten von Flotten:
    <ul><li>Defense Fleets: Jeder [Planet] hat eine Verteidigungs-Flotte. Diese Flotte ist 
    nicht bewegbar und wird nur benutzt wenn der Planet angegriffen wird.</li><li>Bewegbare Flotten: 
    auf deinen [Planets] kannst du 
    Flotten erschafen und sie zum [Travel] zu benutzen im [Universe]</li><li>Ultimate Fleets: Wenn 
    eine Flotte eine [Ultimate] Einheit hat, wird es ultimative Flotte genannt</li></ul><h2>Wie 
    erzeugt man eine Flotte?</h2>
    Als erstes, musst du [CombatUnits] bauen auf den Planeten deiner [PrivateZone]. Wenn sie 
    fertiggestellt sind,
    werden sie in die Verteidigungsflotten des Planeten gestellt. Dann kannst du zu der
    <i>Fleets</i>Sektion von diesem Planeten gehen und eine neue kreieren. Danach bist du in der   
    Lage die [CombatUnits] von der Verdeitungsflotte deines Planeten in eine neue zu bewegen.
    <p>
    Eine [Fleet] kann sich nur bewegen wenn es [CombatUnits] hat und zur Zeit inaktiv ist.
    
    </p><h2>Was können Flotten machen?</h2>
    Die erste Anwendung der Flotte ist zu [Travel](reisen) in deine [PrivateZone]. Mit der 
    [LineOfSight] wirst du in der Lage sein jede Zone zu eforschen. Du wirst auch in der Lage sein  
    [Intrinsic] Ressourcen einzufangen und andere [Planets] zu besiedeln.
 Wenn du bereit bist, kannst du das [WormHole] benutzen um in die [HotZone] zu [Travel](reisen).
    <p>
    In der [HotZone] wirst du in der Lage sein andere Flotten zu attackieren, Planeten mit [Raid] 
    zu plündern, [TradeRoutes] zu machen und vieles mehr. 
    
    </p><h2>Flotten-Fracht</h2>
    Jede Flotte hat einen Frachtraum wo man [Intrinsic] Ressourcen lagern kann. Wenn deine Flotte 
    eine Fracht geladen hat,
    kannst du zu einem Planeten von dir gehen um die Fracht zu den Ressourcen abzuladen. Bemerke dass 
    wenn du angegriffen wirst und verlierst, behält dein Gegner deine Fracht als Beutegut.
    <p>
    Die Verteidigungsflotte deines Heimatplaneten wird auch benutzt Ressourcen zu benutzen die du im 
    [AuctionHouse] kaufst.

    </p><h2>Flotten-Farben</h2>
    In der [Universe] Ansicht wirst du verschiedene [Fleets] mit verschiedenen Farben sehen. Jede 
    Farbe hat ihre eigene Bedeutung, und ist abhängig von deinem diplomatischen Status mit der 
    [Alliance] des jeweiligen Flotten-Besitzers:
    <ul><li>Graue Farbe: du bist neutral für diesen Spieler</li><li>Gelbe Farbe: Du hast einen 
    Null-Agressionen Pakt mit diesem Spieler</li><li>Blaue Farbe: dieser Spieler ist dein 
    Verbündeter</li><li>Rote Farbe: Diese Flotte ist dein Feind!</li></ul></div>");
			Add("en", "FleetContent", @"<h1>Fleets</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    A [Fleet] is a group of [CombatUnits] that can [Travel] on the [Universe]. There are several types of
    fleets:
    <ul><li>Defense Fleets: every [Planet] has a defense fleet. This fleet isn't movable and it's only used
  when the planet is attacked</li><li>Movable Fleets: on your [Planets] you can create fleets and use them to [Travel] on the [Universe]</li><li>Ultimate Fleets: if a fleet has a [Ultimate] unit, it's called a ultimate fleet</li></ul><h2>How to Create a Fleet?</h2>
    First of all, you need to build [CombatUnits] on one of your [PrivateZone] planets. When they're finished,
    they will be placed on the planet's defense fleet. Then you can go the the
    <i>Fleets</i> section of that planet and create a new one. After that you may move [CombatUnits] from the 
    planet's defense fleet info your new fleet.
    <p />
    A [Fleet] can only move if it has [CombatUnits] and it's idle at the moment.
    
    <h2>What can Fleets do?</h2>
    The first usage of a fleet is just to [Travel] on your [PrivateZone]. You'll be able to discover each
    zone because of the fleet's [LineOfSight]. You'll also be able to grab [Intrinsic] resources and colonize
    other [Planets]. When you're up for it, you may use the [WormHole] to [Travel] to the [HotZone].
    <p />
    On the [HotZone] you'll be abble to attack other fleets, [Raid] planets, perform [TradeRoutes] and much more. 
    
    <h2>Fleet's Cargo</h2>
    Each fleet has a cargo hole that can store [Intrinsic] resources. When your fleet has something on the cargo,
    you can go to one of your planets to unload that cargo into your resources. Note that if you're attacked
    and lose, your opponent will earn your cargo as loot.
    <p />
    Your home planet's defense fleet is also used to store resources you buy at the [AuctionHouse].

    <h2>Fleet's Colors</h2>
    On the [Universe] view you'll see several [Fleets] with different colors. Each color has it's own meaning, and
    depends on your diplomatic status with the fleet's owner [Alliance]:
    <ul><li>Color Gray: you are neutral to that player</li><li>Color Yellow: you are on a non aggression pact with that player's alliance</li><li>Color Blue: you are allied with that player</li><li>Color Red: That fleet is your enemy!</li></ul></div>");
			Add("hr", "FleetContent", @"<h1>Flote</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
[Fleet] je grupa [CombatUnits] koje mogu [Travel] u [Universe].Postoji nekoliko tipova flota:
<ul><li>Obranbene flote: svaki [Planet] ima obranbenu flotu. Ova flota je statična i koristi se samo kada je planet napadnut.</li><li>Pokretne Flote: na vašim [Planets] možete stvoriti flote i koristiti se s njima da  [Travel] u  [Universe]</li><li>Ultimateivne Flote: ako flota ima (Ultimativnu jednicu), tada je zvana ultimativna flota </li></ul><h2>Kako Kreirati Flotu?</h2>
Najprije trebate izgraditi CombatUnits] na jednome od vaših [PrivateZone] planeta.
Kada završite, one će biti smještene u obranbenu flotu planeta. Tada mižete ići na <i>Flote</i> sekciju planeta i krerati novu flotu. Nakon toga možete pomaknuti [CombatUnits] iz obrane planeta u vašu novu flotu.
<p />
[Fleet] se može micati samo ako ima [CombatUnits] i u ako miruje u trenutku izdavanja naredbe.

<h2>Što Flote mogu činiti?</h2>
Prva upotreba flote je samo da se [Travel] u vašoj [PrivateZone]. Možete otkiriti svaku zonu zbog [LineOfSight] flote. Također možete zgrabiti [Intrinsic]  resurse i kolonizirati druge [Planets].
Kada ste spremni na to možete se koristiti [WormHole] da [Travel] u [HotZone].
<p />
U [HotZone] možete napadati druge flote, [Raid] planete, izvoditi [TradeRoutes] puno toga više. 

<h2>Teret Flote</h2>
Svaka flota ima teretetni dio koji može skladištiti [Intrinsic] resourse. Kada vaša flota ima nešo u treteu možete krenuti prema nekom od svojih planeta da istovarite taj teret u vaše resurse. Ako ste napadnuti i izgubite, protivnik će dobiti vaš teret kao plijen.
<p />
Obranbena flota vašega početnoga planeta također se služi kao mjesto za skladištnje resusrsa koje kupita u [AuctionHouse].

<h2>Boje Flote</h2>
U [Universe] pogledu vidjeti ćete nekoliko  [Fleets] sa razlićitim bojama. Svaka boja ima svoje značanje i ovisi o vašem diplomatskom statusu sa vlasnikom flote [Alliance]:
<ul><li>Siva boja: neutralni ste sa tim igračom</li><li>Žuta Boja : imate pakt neneapdanja sa savezom toga igrača </li><li>Plava Boja: Vi ste saveznik tome igraču</li><li>Crvena boja: Ta flota je vaš neprijatelj!</li></ul></div>");
			Add("pt", "FleetContent", @"<h1>Armadas</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Uma [Fleet] é um grupo de [CombatUnits] que pode [Travel] no [Universe]. Há vários tipos de armadas:
    <ul><li>
    Armadas de Defesa: Cada [Planet] tem a sua própria armada de defesa. Esta armada não se pode mover
    e só é usada quando o planeta é atacado
  </li><li>Armadas Móveis: nos teus [Planets] podes criar armadas para [Travel] no [Universe]</li><li>Armadas Supremas: se uma armada tem uma unidade [Ultimate], é chamada armada suprema</li></ul><h2>Como criar uma Armada?</h2>
    Em primeiro lugar, é preciso construir [CombatUnits] num dos planetas da tua [PrivateZone]. Quando estiverem
    prontas, serão colocadas na armada de defesa desse planeta. Nessa altura podes ir à secção <i>Armadas</i>
    desse planeta e criar uma nova armada. Podes então mover [CombatUnits] da armada de defesa para a armada
    criada.
    <p />
    Uma [Fleet] só se pode mover se tiver [CombatUnits] e estiver sem nenhuma ordem.

    <h2>O que podem fazer as Armadas?</h2>
    A primeira utilidade de uma armada é apenas [Travel] na tua [PrivateZone]. Serás capaz de descobrir
    a tua zona devido à [LineOfSight] da tua armada. Também poderás apanhar recursos [Intrinsics] e colonizar
    outros [Planets]. Quando estiveres pronto, podes usar o [WormHole] para [Travel] para a [HotZone].
    <p />
    Na [HotZone] serás capaz de atacar outras armadas, fazer [Raid] a planetas, realizar [TradeRoutes]
    e muito mais.

    <h2>Carga de uma Armada</h2>
    Cada armada tem um compartimento que pode armazenar recursos [Intrinsics]. Quando a tua armada tem carga,
    tens de ir a um dos teus planetas para a descarregar para os teus recursos. Nota que se fores atacado e perderes,
    o teu adversário ganha a carga da tua armada como prémio.
    <p />
    A armada de defesa do teu planeta mãe é também usada para armazenar recursos que compras na [AuctionHouse].

    <h2>Cores das Armadas no Universo</h2>
    Na vista do [Universe] podes ver várias [Fleets] com cores diferentes. Cada cor tem ó seu próprio significado
    e depende do teu estado diplomático com a [Alliance] do jogador dono da [Fleet].
    <ul><li>Cor cinzenta: tens uma relação neutra com este jogador</li><li>Cor amarela: estás com um pacto de não agressão com este jogador</li><li>Cor azul: estás aliado com este jogador</li><li>Cor vermelha: estás em guerra com este jogador</li></ul></div>");
			Add("de", "HotZoneContent", @"<h1>Hot Zone</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Die [HotZone] ist wo die ganze Action stattfindet. Dort wirst du andere Spieler finden, andere 
    [Races] und ein enormes [Universe] zu erforschen. In der [HotZone] kann das Spiel dich nicht 
    beschützen gegen andere Gegner, du bist auf dich selbst gestellt. Der einzige Schutz den dir das 
    Spiel bieten kann, ist dass Spieler mit höherem Level nicht in der Lage sind Spieler mit 
    niedrigerem Level anzugreifen.
    <p>
    Aber du musst nicht allein im Universum sein, du solltest einer [Alliance] beitreten für Schutz 
    und Führung. Du solltest auch eine [Profession] suchen und ihre [Quests] folgen, weil du so 
    schneller wachsen kannst.
    </p><p>
    Einige Interessenspunkte die du in der [HotZone] vorfinden magst:
    </p><ul><li>Andere [Planets] zu besiedelen, die es dir erlauben den [Extractor] zu bauen und 
    mehrere seltene Ressourcen zu gewinnen</li><li>
    [WormHole] - es gibt eine enorme Anzahl von Wormholes im Universum, und sie sind sehr nützlich um deine [Travel] Zeit effizient zu verkürzen. 
    </li><li>[Markets] - Finde Märkte und folge den [TradeRoutes] um ein reicher [Merchant] zu 
    werden</li><li>[Arenas] - kämpfe in den Schlachten um einer der obersten [Gladiator] zu 
    werden</li></ul><a id=" + '"' + @"levels" + '"' + @" name=" + '"' + @"levels" + '"' + @"></a><h2>Zone Level</h2>
    Jedes Element im Universum hat ein eigenes Level, das abhängig ist von von der eigenen Zone. 
    [Planets], [Arenas], [Markets], [Relics], etc.
    Je näher du zum Zentrum bist, umso grösser ist das Level der Zone. Die Zone im Zentrum heisst
    <i>Sirius</i>.
    <p>
    Diese Zone Levels sind dazu da um folgendes sichern:
    </p><ul><li>Wenn ein Spieler ein Spiel anfängt, hat er ein privates [WormHole] das seine 
    [PrivateZone] mit einem [WormHole] des äusseren Universums verbindet. Von dort aus, kann er sich 
    zum Zentrum bewegen um bessere [Planets] zu erobern</li><li>Das bedeutet das der Spieler in den 
    äusseren <i>rings</i> anfängt sich zum Zentrum durchzuarbeiten</li><li>Und auch dass Anfänger
    Spieler sich mit fortgeschrittenen Spielern nicht kreuzen, weil diese sich bereits in bessere 
    Position begeben haben </li></ul>
    Levels variieren von 1 to 10, indem 10 das reichste/mächtigste ist. Das folgende Bild ist eine
    Darstellung des [OB] Universums:
  </div>");
			Add("en", "HotZoneContent", @"<h1>Hot Zone</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    The [HotZone] is where all the action occurs. There you'll find other players, other [Races] and
    a vast [Universe] to explore. On the [HotZone] the game doesn't protect you against other players,
    you're on your own. The only protection the game provides, is that higher level players won't be
    able to attack low level players.
    <p />
    But you don't need to be alone on the universe, you should get an [Alliance] for protection
    and guidance. You should also choose a [Profession] and follow its [Quests], because you'll grow
    faster that way.
    <p />
    Some points of interest that you may find on the [HotZone]:
    <ul><li>Other [Planets] to colonize, that will allow you to build the [Extractor] and earn rare resources</li><li>
    [WormHole] - there's a vast number of wormholes on the universe, and they are very useful to decrease
    your [Travel] time efficiently
  </li><li>[Markets] - find markets and follow [TradeRoutes] to be a rich [Merchant]</li><li>[Arenas] - battle on the arenas to become the supreme [Gladiator]</li></ul><a id=" + '"' + @"levels" + '"' + @" name=" + '"' + @"levels" + '"' + @"></a><h2>Zone Level</h2>
    Every universe body has its own level, that depends on its zone. [Planets], [Arenas], [Markets], [Relics], etc.
    The more to the center you are, the greater the zone level is. The center zone is called <i>Sirius</i>.
    <p />
    These zone levels exist to provide the following flows:
    <ul><li>When a player starts the game, he has a private [WormHole] that connects its [PrivateZone] to a
  [WormHole] on the outer universe. From there, he can move to the center to obtain better [Planets]</li><li>This means that players start on the outer <i>rings</i> and work their way to the center</li><li>And also that rookie players shouldn't come to face more advanced players, because the advanced
  players had already moved to better positions</li></ul>
    Levels vary from 1 to 10, being 10 the most rich/powerful. The following image is a representation of
    the [OB] universe:
  </div>");
			Add("hr", "HotZoneContent", @"<h1>Hot Zone</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
[HotZone] je mjesto gdje se dešava sva akcija. Tamo ćete pronći druge igrače, druge [Races] i ogromni [Universe] za istražiti.U [HotZone] igra vas ne štiti do drugih igrača, prepušteni ste sami sebi.
Jedina zaštita koju igra pruža je da igrači višeg nivoa ne mogu napadati igrače niskog nivoa.
<p />
Ali ne trebate biti sami u svemiru, trebate nabaviti [Alliance] za zaštitu i vodstvo. Također trebate odabrati [Profession] i slijediti njezine  [Quests], zato jer ćete tako brže rasti.
<p />
Neke interesante točke koje možete promaći u [HotZone]:
<ul><li>Druge [Planets] za kolonitzirati, koji će vam dopoustiti da izgradite [Extractor] i zradite rijetke resurse</li><li>
[WormHole] - postoji velik broj crvotočina u svemiru, i one su jako korisne da efikasno  smanje vrijeme vašeg [Travel]
</li><li>[Markets] - pronađite markete i slijedite  [TradeRoutes] da budete bogati [Merchant]</li><li>[Arenas] - borite se u arenama da budete najjači Gladiator]</li></ul><a id=" + '"' + @"levels" + '"' + @" name=" + '"' + @"levels" + '"' + @"></a><h2>Zone Level</h2>
Svako svemirsko tijelo ima svoj nivo, što je veći nivo zone. [Planets], [Arenas], [Markets], [Relics], itd. Centar se zove <i>Sirius</i>.
<p />
Ovi nivoi zona postoje da daju sljedeće tokove:
<ul><li>Kada igrač započne igru, ima privatnu [WormHole] koja povezuje njegovu [PrivateZone] sa
[WormHole] u vanjskom svemiru. Od tamo on se miče prema centru da dobije bolje [Planets]</li><li>Ovo znači da taj igrač počinje na vanjskim <i>rings</i> i napreduje prema centru</li><li>Također da početnici se ne suočavaju odmah sa naprednijim igračima jer su napredniji igrači već otišli na bolje pozicije</li></ul>
Nivoi variraiju od 1 do 10, sa 10 koji su najbogatiji/najmoćniji. Sljedeća slika predstavlja [OB] svemir:
</div>");
			Add("pt", "HotZoneContent", @"<h1>Zona Pública</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    A [HotZone] é onde toda a acção se passa. Lá encontrarás outros jogadores, outras [Races] e um
    vasto [Universe] para explorar. Na [HotZone] o jogo não te protege contra outros jogadores, estás
    por tua conta e risco, A única protecção que o jogo dá, é que jogadores de nível mais alto não
    podem atacar jogadores de nível mais baixo.
    <p />
    Mas não precisas de estar sozinho no universo, podes entrar para uma [Alliance] para protecção
    e ajuda. Também deves escolher uma [Profession] e seguir as suas [Quests], porque desta forma
    serás capaz de evoluir mais rapidamente.
    <p />
    Alguns pontos de interesse que poderás encontrar na [HotZone]:
    <ul><li>Outros [Planets] para colonizar, que te permitirão construir o [Extractor], que te dá acesso a recursos raross</li><li>
    [WormHole] - Há uma vasta rede de túneis espalhados pelo universo, e quantos mais conheceres,
    mais rápido conseguirás [Travel]
  </li><li>[Markets] - Encontra mercados para efecturares [TradeRoutes] e torna-te num [Merchant] rico</li><li>[Arenas] - Batalha nas arenas para te tornares no [Gladiator] supremo</li></ul><a id=" + '"' + @"levels" + '"' + @" name=" + '"' + @"levels" + '"' + @"></a><h2>Nível de Zona</h2>
  Todos os elementos no universeo têm um nível, que depende da zona onde estão. Isto é válido para
  [Planets], [Arenas], [Markets], [Relics], etc. Quanto mais para o centro, maior o nível será. A zona do centro
  é chamada <i>Sirius</i>.
    <p />
    Esta lógica de zonas existe para providenciar o seguinte:
    <ul><li>
    Quando um jogador começa o jogo, ele tem um [WormHole] privado que liga a sua [PrivateZone] a um
    outro [WormHole] na extremidade do universo. Daí, ele pode mover-se para o centro para obter
    [Planets] melhores.
  </li><li>
    Isto significa que os jogadores começam na extremidade do universo, e à medida que vão evoluindo, vão
    migrando mais para o centro.
  </li><li>
    E assim acontece que jogadores mais recentes não vão chocar com jogadores mais avançados, porque
    os jogadores avançados já se moveram para zonas melhores.
  </li></ul>
    Os níveis variam entre 1 e 10, sendo 10 o melhor. A seguinte imagem é uma representação do universo
    do [OB]:
  </div>");
			Add("de", "LineOfSightContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
   [LineOfSight] ist das sichtbare Gebiet das etwas was in deinem Besitz ist umgibt. z.B. (eine [Flotte], ein [Planet], etc). In diese, Gebiet kannst du alles sehen was sich bewegt, inklusive der feindlichen Einheiten.
   <p>
   Es gibt 3 verschieden Arten von [LineOfSight]:
   </p><p></p><ul><li>
 [LineOfSight] ein Viereck um deine [Flotte] herum. Diese [LineOfSight] kommt in [Flotten] vor die nur [Light] Einheiten haben.<p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 1 Square Around" + '"' + @" /></p></li><li>
 [LineOfSight] zwei Vierecke um deine [Flotte] oder [Planet]  herum. Die [LineOfSight] kommt vor in [Flotte]n mit mindestens , eine [Medium] oder [Heavy] Einheit und [Planet].<p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 2 Square Around" + '"' + @" /></p></li><li>
 [LineOfSight] drei Vierecke um den [Beacon] herum :<p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight3.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 3 Squares Around" + '"' + @" /></p></li></ul><p></p></div>");
			Add("en", "LineOfSightContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
   [LineOfSight] is the visible area around something that belongs to you (a [Fleet], a [Planet], etc). In this area you can see everything that is moving 
   including enemy units.
   <p />
   There are 3 types of [LineOfSight]:
   <p /><ul><li>
 [LineOfSight] one square arround the [Fleet]. This [LineOfSight] is present in [Fleets] with only [Light] units.<p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 1 Square Around" + '"' + @" /></li><li>
 [LineOfSight] two squares arround the some element in the Universe. This [LineOfSight] is present in [Fleet]s with, at least, one [Medium] or [Heavy] unit and in [Planet].<p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 2 Square Around" + '"' + @" /></li><li>
 [LineOfSight] three squares arround the [Beacon]:<p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight3.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 3 Squares Around" + '"' + @" /></li></ul><p /></div>");
			Add("hr", "LineOfSightContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
[LineOfSight] je vidljivo područje oko nečega što pripada vama ([Fleet], [Planet], itd). Unutar ovoga područja možete vidjeti sve što se miče, uključujući neprijateljske jedinice.
<p />
Postoje tri tipa [LineOfSight]:
<p /><ul><li>
[LineOfSight] jedan kvadrat oko [Fleet]. Ovaj [LineOfSight] je prisutan u flotama sa samo [Light] jedinicama <p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 1 Square Around" + '"' + @" /></li><li>
[LineOfSight] dva kvadrata oko nekog elementa u Svemiru. Ovaj [LineOfSight] je prisutan u [Fleet] sa barem jednom [Medium] ili [Heavy] jednicom i na [Planet].<p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 2 Square Around" + '"' + @" /></li><li>
[LineOfSight] tri kvadrata oko [Beacon]:<p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight3.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 3 Squares Around" + '"' + @" /></li></ul><p /></div>");
			Add("pt", "LineOfSightContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    A [LineOfSight] é a área visivel à volta de algo que te pertence (uma [Fleet], uma [Planet], etc). Nesta área podes ver tudo o que se move incluindo unidades 
    inimigas.
   <p />
   Existem 3 tipos de [LineOfSight]:
   <p /><ul><li>
 [LineOfSight] uma quadrícula à volta de uma [Fleet]. Este [LineOfSight] está presente em [Fleets] que possuam apenas [LightUnits].<p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 1 Square Around" + '"' + @" /></li><li>
 [LineOfSight] duas quadrículas à volta de uma [Fleet] (ou [Planet]):<p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 2 Square Around" + '"' + @" /></li><li>
 [LineOfSight] três quadrículas à volta de um [Beacon]:<p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/LineOfSight3.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Line of Sight 3 Squares Around" + '"' + @" /></li></ul><p /></div>");
			Add("de", "PirateBayManual", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PirateBay.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"float: right;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Pirate Bay" + '"' + @" />
    Die Bucht der Piraten ist ein Universum Gebäube das 2 Zwecken dient:
    <ul><li>Als erstes den Spielern zu helfen die Piraten sind, die Flotten die Ressourcen in ihrer Fracht haben und Planeten ohne Verteidigungsflotte aufzuspüren.</li><li>Als zweites Missionen zu liefern die mit gewissen Fraktionen zu tun haben. Zum Beispiel Space Force Missionen werden in der Bucht der Piraten abgeliefert.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("en", "PirateBayManual", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PirateBay.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"float:right;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Pirate Bay" + '"' + @" />
    The Pirate Bay is a universe building that serves 2 Proposes:
    <ul><li>The first is to help players that have the Pirate profession to track Fleets with resouces in their cargo and planets with no defense fleet.</li><li>The second is to deliver quests that are relacted to certain factions. For instance Space Force's quests are delivered at the Pirate Bay.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("hr", "PirateBayManual", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PirateBay.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"float:right;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Pirate Bay" + '"' + @" />
Piratski dok je svemirska zgrada koja služi za 2 svrhe: 
 <ul><li> Prva je da pomaže igračima koji imaju profesiju Pirat da prate Flote sa resursima u njihovim skladištima i planete bez obranbene flote.</li><li> Druga je da dostavi misije koje su povezane za određene fakcije. Naprimjer misije Svemirskih Snaga su dostavljene u Piratski Dok.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("pt", "PirateBayManual", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PirateBay.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"float:right;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Pirate Bay" + '"' + @" />
    A Baía de Piratas é um edificio no universo que serve 2 propósitos:
    <ul><li>O primeiro é ajudar os jogadores que têm a profissão de Piratas a procurar planetas sem armada de defesa e armadas com recursos na carga.</li><li>O segundo é servirem como ponto de entrega de missões que estão relacionadas com certas facções. Por exemplo, as missões relativas à Space Force são entregues nas Baías de Piratas.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("de", "PlanetsContent", @"<h1>Planeten</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Die Planeten sind das Herz und die Seele deines Imperiums. Sie versorgen dich mit [Intrinsic] Ressourcen, du kannst Planeten
    [Facilities]bauen, und sie erlauben dir auch [CombatUnits] zu bauen. Je mehr Planeten du hast 
 umso mächtiger wirst du sein. Du kannst zwei Arten von Planeten haben: Planeten in der 
    [PrivateZone] und Planeten in der [HotZone].
    
    <h2>Private Zone Planeten</h2>
    Die Planeten in deiner [PrivateZone] sind die wichtigsten.Sie haben all die Hauptgebäude und du 
    wirst sie niemals verlieren können, als vergiss nicht sie zu aufzubessern. Diese Planeten sind 
    auch die einzigen die es dir erlauben [CombatUnits] zu bauen.
    <p>
    Das einzige Problem mit den Planeten der [PrivateZone] ist dass sie keine seltenen [Intrinsics] 
 generieren können. Du musst dich in die [HotZone] begeben um sie zu bekommen.
    
    </p><h2>Hot Zone Planeten</h2>
    Planeten in der [HotZone] sind ähnlich zu Minen. Si sind sehr einfach, und du kannst nur wenige 
    Gebäude auf ihnen bauen (zum Beispiel, der [Extractor]) und sie können attackiert (siehe
    [UniverseAttack]) und geplündert
    (siehe [Raid]) werden von anderen Spielern.
    <p>
    Trotz der Risiken, diese Planeten sind essentiell, weil sie dich mit seltenen Ressourcen 
    versorgen: [Astatine],
    [Cryptium], [Argon], [Radon] and [Prismal]. Du kannst sie über das [Extractor] Gebäude kriegen. 
    Ohne diese seltenen Ressourcen wirst du nicht in der Lage sein Gebäude aufzurüsten oder mächtige 
    [CombatUnits] zu bauen.
    </p><p>
    Du kannst ein Maximum von 8 Planeten in der [HotZone] haben. Jeder Planet in der [HotZone]hat ein 
    [ZoneLevel]. 
    Je höher der Zone Level, umso mehr Ressourcen wirst du mit dem [Extractor] sammeln können.

    <a name=" + '"' + @"Capacity" + '"' + @" id=" + '"' + @"Capacity" + '"' + @"></a></p><h2>Resource Limit</h2>
    Jeder Planet hat seine eigenen Attribute die dein Ressourcen-Einkommen alle 10 Minuten erhöhen. 
    Alle diese Ressourcen sind global zu allen deinen Planeten, aber du hast einen Limit. Deine
    Ressourcen nicht über dein Ressourcen-Limit steigen. Um dein Ressourcen-Limit zu erhöhen   
    kannst du:
    <ul><li>Wenn deine Rasse die [LightHumans] ist, musst du ein [Silo] bauen und das [CommandCenter]</li><li>Wenn deine Rasse die [DarkHumans] ist, musst du das [SlaveWarehouse] bauen und [DarknessHall]</li><li>Wenn deine Rasse die [Bugs] ist, musst du das [Nest] bauen</li></ul></div>");
			Add("en", "PlanetsContent", @"<h1>Planets</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    The planets are the heart and soul of your empire. They provide you with [Intrinsic] resources, you can build
    [Facilities] on them, and they also allow you to build [CombatUnits]. The more planets you have, the more
    powerfull you will be. You can have two types of planets: planets on your [PrivateZone] and planets on the
    [HotZone].
    
    <h2>Private Zone Planets</h2>
    The planets on your [PrivateZone] are the most important. They have all the major facilities and you'll
    never be able to lose them, so be sure to improve them. These planets are also the only ones that
    allow you to build [CombatUnits].
    <p />
    The only problem with [PrivateZone] planets is that they can't generate rare [Intrinsics]. You'll need
    to get to the [HotZone] to get them.
    
    <h2>Hot Zone Planets</h2>
    Planets on the [HotZone] are similar to mines. They are very simple, you can only build a few facility types
    on them (for example, the [Extractor]) and they can be attacked (see [UniverseAttack]) and raided 
    (see [Raid]) by other players.
    <p />
    However the risks, these planets are essential, because they provide you with rare resources: [Astatine],
    [Cryptium], [Argon], [Radon] and [Prismal]. You can get them via the [Extractor] facility. Without these
    rare resources you won't be able to upgrade facilities or build powerful [CombatUnits].
    <p />
    You can have a maximum of eight planets on the [HotZone]. Each planet on the [HotZone] has a [ZoneLevel]. 
    The higher the zone level, the more resources you'll be able to gather via the [Extractor].

    <a name=" + '"' + @"Capacity" + '"' + @" id=" + '"' + @"Capacity" + '"' + @"></a><h2>Resource Limit</h2>
    Each planet has its own modifiers that increase your resource income every ten minutes. All those resources
    are global to all your planets, but you have a limit. Your resources won't grow beyong your current
    resource limit. To increase your resource limit you can:
    <ul><li>If your your race is [LightHumans], you must build the [Silo] and the [CommandCenter]</li><li>If your race is [DarkHumans], you must build the [SlaveWarehouse] and the [DarknessHall]</li><li>If your race is [Bugs], you must build the [Nest]</li></ul></div>");
			Add("hr", "PlanetsContent", @"<h1>Planeti</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
Planeti su srce i duša vašega carstva. Oni vam daju [Intrinsic] resurse, možete graditi [Facilities] na njima, i oni također dopuštaju gradnju [CombatUnits]. Što više planeta imate, to ćete biti jači. Možete imati dva tipa planeta: planete u vašoj  [PrivateZone] i planete u [HotZone].
<h2> Planeti Privatne Zone </h2>
Planeti u vašoj [PrivateZone] su najvažniji. Oni svi imaju glavna postrojenja i nikada ih ne možete izgubiti, zato se pobrinite da ih unaprijedite. Ovi planeti su također jedini koju dopuštaju izgradnju [CombatUnits].
<p />
Jedini problem sa [PrivateZone] planetima je da oni ne mogu generirati rijetke [Intrinsics]. Trebate doći na [HotZone] da ih dobijete.

<h2>Hot Zone Planeti</h2>
Planeti u [HotZone] su slični rudnicima. Oni su jako jednostavni, možete graditi nekoliko tipova postrojenja na njima (na primjer, [Extractor]) i oni mogu biti napadnuti (vidi [UniverseAttack]) i opljačkani  (vidi [Raid]) od strne drugih igrača.
<p />
No unatoč riziku, ovi planeti su esencijalni, zato jer vam daju rijetke resurse: [Astatine],
    [Cryptium], [Argon], [Radon] and [Prismal]. Možete ih dobiti preko [Extractor] postrojenja. Bez ovih rijetkih resursa nećete moći unaprijediti postrojenja ili graditi moćne [CombatUnits].
<p />
Možete imati maksimalno osam planeta na [HotZone]. Svaki planet na [HotZone] ima [ZoneLevel].
Što je veći nivo zone, više resursa ćete moći prikupiti preko [Extractor].
<a name=" + '"' + @"Capacity" + '"' + @" id=" + '"' + @"Capacity" + '"' + @"></a><h2> Limit Resursa</h2>
Svaki planet ima svoje vlastite modifikatore koji povećavaju prihod resursa svakih 10 minuta. Svi ti resursi su globalni svim vašim planetima, ali imate limit. Resursi neće rasti preko vašeg trenutačnog limita. Da povećate limit vaših resursa  možete:
<ul><li>Ako je vaša rasa [LightHumans], morate izgraditi [Silo] i [CommandCenter]</li><li>Ako je vaša rasa [DarkHumans], morate izgraditi [SlaveWarehouse] i [DarknessHall]</li><li>Ako je vaša rasa [Bugs], morate izgraditi [Nest]</li></ul></div>");
			Add("pt", "PlanetsContent", @"<h1>Planetas</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Os planetas são a alma do teu império. Eles fornecem recursos [Intrinsics], possibilitam-te a construção de
    [Facilities] e permitem-te construir [CombatUnits]. Quanto mais planetas tiveres, mais poderoso serás. Podes
    ter dois tipos de planetas: planetas na tua [PrivateZone] e planetas na [HotZone].

    <h2>Planetas da Zona Privada</h2>
    Os planetas na tua [PrivateZone] são os mais importantes. Neles podes costruir a maior parte dos edifícios
    e ainda por cima nunca os perderás, por isso aposta bem neles. Estes planetas são tanbém os únicos que te
    permitem construir [CombatUnits].
    <p />
    A única desvantagem dos planetas da [PrivateZone] é que não conseguem gerar recursos raros. Terás de ir
    para a [HotZone] para os obteres.

    <h2>Planetas da Zona Pública</h2>
    Os planetas na [HotZone] são idênticos a minas. São muito simples, é somente possível construir um número
    limitado de edifícios (como por exemplo o [Extractor]), e podem ser atacados (ver [UniverseAttack]) e 
    pilhados (ver [Raid]) por outros jogadores.
    <p />
    Apesar dos riscos, estes planetas são essenciais, porque fornecem-te com recursos raros, nomeadamente:
    [Astatine], [Cryptium], [Argon], [Radon] e [Prismal]. Podes obter estes recursos por intermédio do edifício
    [Extractor]. Sem estes recursos raros não serás capaz de evoluir os teus edifícios e construir [CombatUnits]
    mais poderosas.
    <p />
    Nota que só podes ter um máximo de oito planetas na [HotZone]. Cada planeta na [HotZone] tem um [ZoneLevel].
    Quanto maior o nível, maior será a quantidade re recursos que poderás obter através do [Extractor].

    <a name=" + '"' + @"Capacity" + '"' + @" id=" + '"' + @"Capacity" + '"' + @"></a><h2>Limite de Recursos</h2>
    Em cada planeta tens um rendimento por recurso a cada dez minutos. Estes rendimentos vão para o teu repositório
    de recursos, que é global a todos os planetas. Contudo, esse repositório tem um limite. Os teus recursos
    não vão passar desse limite, pelo que o tens de aumentar quando necessário. Para o fazer:
    <ul><li>Se fores da raça [LightHumans], tens de construir o [Silo] e o [CommandCenter]</li><li>Se fores da raça [DarkHumans], tens de construir o [SlaveWarehouse] e a [DarknessHall]</li><li>Se fores da raça [Bugs], tens de construir o [Nest]</li></ul></div>");
			Add("de", "PrivateZoneContent", @"<h1>Private Zone</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Die [PrivateZone] ist der Ort wo du das Spiel anfängst. Es ist eine Zone die nur dir zugänglich 
    ist, kein anderer Spieler vermag deine [PrivateZone] zu betreten. In deiner [PrivateZone] hast du 
    fünf [Planets]. Diese sind deine Haupt-Planeten wo du [Intrinsic] Ressourcen erhalten 
    und [CombatUnits] bauen kannst.
    <p>
    Hier ist ein Bild von deiner Private Zone wenn das Spiel anfängt:
    <img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PZ1.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Bild der Private Zone" + '"' + @" />

    Und hier ist ein Bild von einer komplett erforschten Private Zone:
    <img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PZ2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Bild der Private Zone" + '"' + @" />
    
    In deiner Privat Zone (und im ganzen Universum) bist du in der Lage verschiedene [Intrinsic] 
    Ressourcen zu finden, die es dir erlauben Ressourcen einzusammeln nur indem du deine [Fleets] 
    zu dieser Position bewegst. 
    Wenn du das Spiel anfängst, sorge dafür dass du sie alle einsammelst, weil du sie später alle 
    brauchen wirst.
    </p><p>
    Wenn du bereit bist deine Private Zone zu verlassen, kannst du das [WormHole] benutzen um in die  
    [HotZone] zu reisen und mit anderen Spielern zu interagieren, weitere Planeten zu besiedeln, und
    vieles mehr.
    </p><p>
    Während du in deiner Private Zone bist, sorge dafür dass du folgende [Quests] folgst:
    </p><ul><li>[GetAllPrivateZoneResources]</li><li>[ColonizeOnePlanetQuest]</li><li>[ColonizeAllPrivateZonePlanetsQuest]</li><li>[FindPrivateWormHoleQuest]</li></ul></div>");
			Add("en", "PrivateZoneContent", @"<h1>Private Zone</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    The [PrivateZone] is the place where you start the game. It's a zone that is only available to you,
    no other players may enter your [PrivateZone]. On your [PrivateZone] you have five [Planets]. These are
    your main planets where you'll be able to get [Intrinsic] resources and build [CombatUnits].
    <p />
    Here's a picture of a private zone when the game starts:
    <img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PZ1.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Private Zone Image" + '"' + @" />

    And here's a picture of a full discovered private zone:
    <img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PZ2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Private Zone Image" + '"' + @" />
    
    On your private zone (and all over the universe) you'll be able to find several [Intrinsic] resources,
    that you'll be able to gather just my moving a [Fleet] to that position. When you start the game,
    be sure to grab them all, because you'll need them.
    <p />
    When you're ready to leave your private zone, you can use the [WormHole] to travel to the [HotZone] and
    interact with other players, colonize more planets, and much more.
    <p />
    While you're on the private zone, be sure to follow the following [Quests]:
    <ul><li>[GetAllPrivateZoneResources]</li><li>[ColonizeOnePlanetQuest]</li><li>[ColonizeAllPrivateZonePlanetsQuest]</li><li>[FindPrivateWormHoleQuest]</li></ul></div>");
			Add("hr", "PrivateZoneContent", @"<h1>Private Zone</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
[PrivateZone] je mjsesto gdje počinjete igru. To je zona koja je dostpna samo vama, niti jedan drugi igrač ne može ući u vašu [PrivateZone]. U vašoj [PrivateZone] imate pet [Planets]. Ovo su vaši glavni planeti gdje možete dobiti [Intrinsic] resurse i izgradti [CombatUnits].
<p />
Ovdje  je slika privatne zone kada igra počne:
<img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PZ1.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Private Zone Image" + '"' + @" />

A ovdje je slika potpuno otkrivene privatne zone:
<img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PZ2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Private Zone Image" + '"' + @" />

U vašoj privatnoj zoni (i čitavom otkrivenom) svemiru moći ćete pronaći nekoliko [Intrinsic] resursa, koje možete prikipiti pokretanjem [Fleet] na tu poziciju. Kada počnete igru, budite sigurni da ih ugrabite sve jer ih trebate.
<p />
Kada ste spremni za napustiti vašu privatnu zonu, možete se poslužiti sa [WormHole] sa putujete u [HotZone] i ineraktirate s drugim igračima, kolonizirate još planeta, i puno toga više.
<p />
Dok ste u privatnoj zoni, budite sigurni da slijedite sljedeće [Quests]:
<ul><li>[GetAllPrivateZoneResources]</li><li>[ColonizeOnePlanetQuest]</li><li>[ColonizeAllPrivateZonePlanetsQuest]</li><li>[FindPrivateWormHoleQuest]</li></ul></div>");
			Add("pt", "PrivateZoneContent", @"<h1>Zona Privada</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    A [PrivateZone] é o sítio onde começas o jogo. É uma zona que só está disponível para ti, outros jogadores
    não conseguem entrar na tua [PrivateZone]. Na tua [PrivateZone] tens cinco [Planets]. Estes serão os teus
    planetas principais onde conseguirás obter recursos [Intrinsics] e construir [CombatUnits].
    <p />
    Esta é uma imagem da tua zona privada quando o jogo começa:
    <img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PZ1.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Imagem da Zona Privada" + '"' + @" />

    E esta é uma imagem de uma zona privada já toda descoberta:
    <img class=" + '"' + @"block" + '"' + @" src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PZ2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Imagem da Zona Privada" + '"' + @" />

    Na tua zona privada (e em todo o universo), vais encontrar recursos [Intrinsics] que podes apanhar simplesmente
    movendo a tua [Fleet] para a sua posição. Quando começas o jogo, certifica-te que os apanhas todos, pois
    vais precisar.
    <p />
    Quando estiveres pronto para sair da tua zona privada, podes usar o [WormHole] para viajar para a 
    [HotZone] e interagir com outros jogadores, colonizar mais planetas, e muito mais.
    <p />
    Mas enquanto estás na tua zona privada, não te esqueças de seguir as seguintes [Quests]:
    <ul><li>[GetAllPrivateZoneResources]</li><li>[ColonizeOnePlanetQuest]</li><li>[ColonizeAllPrivateZonePlanetsQuest]</li><li>[FindPrivateWormHoleQuest]</li></ul></div>");
			Add("de", "RaidManual", @"<h1>Plündern</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Plündern besteht aus dem Angreifen eines [Planet] des anderen Spielers mit der einzigen Absicht 
    [Intrinsic] Ressourcen zu stehlen
    Diese Aktion wird üblicherweise von [Pirate] Spielern auf ihren [Quests] durchgefürt, kann aber 
    auch von jedem anderen Spieler durchgeführt werden.
    <p>
    Wenn du einen Planeten plünderst, können zwei Dinge passieren:
    </p><ul><li>Die [Fleet] der Verteidigung des Planeten ist leer und das Plündern wird 
    durchgeführt</li><li>
    Der Planet hat ein paar wenige Verteidigunsmöglichkeiten und eine Schlacht auf dem [GameBoard]; 
    wird angefangen; nur wenn du gewinnst iwird die Plünderung durchgeführt.
 </li></ul>
    Aber auch wenn die Plünderung durchgeführt wird, kannst es passieren dass du überhaupt keine 
    Ressourcen kriegst. Es gibt einen Timeout für das Plündern um Missbrauch zu verhindrn, und so ist 
    es nur möglich einen Planeten alle 14 Stunden zu plündern.
    <p>
    Wenn die Plünderung erfolgreich war, das wirst du einigen Ressourcen stehlen können und dein 
    [Pirate] Rang wird erhöht. Du wirst zwei verschiedene Arten von Ressourcen stehlen. Eine 
    Ressource nach zufälliger Auswahl und die andere ist die, die der Besitzer des Zielplaneten am 
    meisten zu Verfügung steht. Und das ist unterschiedlich für jede [Race]:
    </p><ul><li>Wenn du einen [LightHumans] Planeten anvisierst, erhälst du [Argon]</li><li>Wenn du 
    einen [DarkHumans] Planeten anvisierst, erhälst du [Cryptium]</li><li>Wenn du einen[Bugs] 
    Planeten anvisierst, erhälst du [Prismal]</li></ul>
    Die gestohlene Quantität ist eine kleiner Prozentsatz des Totalbetrags des Zielspielers, and 
    Planeten mit höherem Level bieten bessere Prozentsätze.
   </div>");
			Add("en", "RaidManual", @"<h1>Raids</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    A raid consists on attacking another player's [Planet] with the sole purpose of stealing [Intrinsic]
    resources. This action is usually performed by [Pirate] players on their [Quests], but can also be done
    by anyone else.
    <p />
    When you raid a planet, two things can occur:
    <ul><li>The planet's defense [Fleet] is empty and the raid is performed</li><li>
  The planet has some defenses and a battle will be started on the [GameBoard]; only if you win
  the raid is performed
 </li></ul>
    Even if the raid is performed, you may not get any resources at all. There is a raid timeout to prevent
    abuse, so it's only possible to raid a planet every ~14 hours.
    <p />
    If the raid is successufully performed, you will get some resources stolen and your [Pirate] ranking
    increased. You will steal two types of resources. One resource picked randomly and the other ressource
    is the one that the target planet's player has the most. And that varies by [Race]:
    <ul><li>If you're targeting a [LightHumans] planet, you'll get [Argon]</li><li>If you're targeting a [DarkHumans] planet, you'll get [Cryptium]</li><li>If you're targeting a [Bugs] planet, you'll get [Prismal]</li></ul>
    The stolen quantity is a small percentage of the target player's total amount, and higher level planets
    provide better percentages.
   </div>");
			Add("hr", "RaidManual", @"<h1>Raids</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
Pljačkanje se sastoji od napadanja [Planet] drugog igrača sa jedniom svrhom kranja [Intrinsic]
resursa. Ova akcija je uobičajeno izvedena od strane [Pirate] igrača na njihovim [Quests], ali također može biti učinjena od bilo koga drugoga.
<p />
Kada pljačkate planet dvije stvari se mogu desiti:
<ul><li>Planetarna obranbrna [Fleet] je prazna i pljačkanje se izvodi</li><li>
Planet ima neku obranu i bitka počinje na [GameBoard]; samo ako pobijedite pljačkanje se izvodi.
</li></ul>
Čak i ako se pljačkanje uspješno izuvede, možda nećete dobiti niti jedan resurs. Postoji timeout pljačko da se spriječi iskorištavanje, tako da je moguće pljačkati planet svako ~14 sati
<p />
Ako je pljačka uspješno izvršena, neki resursi će biti ukradeni i vaš [Pirate] će narasti. Ukrasti ćete dva tipa resursa. Jedan resurs odabran odabran slučajno i drugi je resurs kojega ciljani planet ima najviše. I to varira po [Race]: <ul><li>Ako vam je meta [LightHumans] planet, dobit ćete[Argon]</li><li>Ako vam je meta [DarkHumans] planet, dobit ćete[ [Cryptium]</li><li>Ako vam je meta [Bugs] planet, dobit ćete[ [Prismal]</li></ul>
Ukradena količina je mali postotak totalne količine ciljanog igrača, i planeti većeg nivoa daju bolji postotak.
</div>");
			Add("pt", "RaidManual", @"<h1>Pilhagens</h1><div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Uma pilhagem consiste em atacar um planeta de outro jogador com o objectivo de roubar recursos [Intrinsics].
    Esta acção é normalmente feita por jogadores [Pirate] nas suas [Quests], mas pode ser feita por qualquer
    jogador, independentemente da sua [Profession].
    <p />
    Quando pilhas um planeta, duas coisas podem acontecer:
    <ul><li>A [Fleet] de defesa do planeta está vazia, e a pilhagem é efectuada</li><li>
  O planeta tem defesas e é começada uma batalha no [GameBoard]; só se a ganhares é que a pilhagem
  é efectuada
 </li></ul>
    Mesmo que a pilhagem seja efectuada, isso não significa que obtenhas recursos. Há um tempo de intervalo
    entre pilhagens para evitar abusos, pelo que só é possível pilhar com sucesso a cada ~14 horas.
    <p />
    Se a pilhagem tiver sucesso, então serão roubados alguns recursos e a tua reputação como [Pirate] é aumentada.
    É possível roubar vários recursos, mas provavelmente só irás roubar o recurso mais comum para o dono do
    planeta que pilhaste, e isso depende da sua [Race]:
    <ul><li>Se atacaste um planeta de [LightHumans] vais obter [Argon]</li><li>Se atacaste um planeta de [DarkHumans] vais obter [Cryptium]</li><li>Se atacaste um planeta de [Bugs] vais obter [Prismal]</li></ul>
    A quantidade do recurso que é roubada é uma percentagem da quantidade total que esse jogador tiver.
    Planetas de nível superior têm percentagens mais elevadas.
   </div>");
			Add("de", "TravelContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Wenn du [Travel] im Universum machen willst, brauchst du nur eine Sache: Eine [Flotte] mit 
    Einheiten. 
    <p>
    Das folgende Bild ist das anfägliche Stadium deiner [PrivateZone] wo eine bewegbare [Fleet] bereit 
    ist sich in Bewegung zu setzten.
    </p><p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PrivateZoneInitialState.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Anfängliches Stadium deiner Private Zone" + '"' + @" /></p><p>
    Um die Flotte zu bewegen klicke einfach drauf und dann klicke auf eine unerforschte Gegend. Dann
    wähle die Option " + '"' + @"Flotte bewegen" + '"' + @". Das folgende Video wird dir zeigen wie:
    </p><p></p></div>");
			Add("en", "TravelContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    If you want to [Travel] in the universe you only need one thing: a [Fleet] with units. 
    <p />
    The Following image is the initial state of your [PrivateZone] where a moveable [Fleet] is ready to move.
    <p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PrivateZoneInitialState.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Initial state of your Private Zone" + '"' + @" /><p />
    To move the fleet simply click on it and them click on a discovered area. Them choose the option " + '"' + @"Move Fleet" + '"' + @". The following video will show you how:
    <p /></div>");
			Add("hr", "TravelContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
Ako želite [Travel] u svemiru trebate samo jednu stvar: [Fleet] sa jedinicama.
<p />
Sljedeća slika je početno stanje vaše [PrivateZone] gdje [Fleet] sa spososbnosti pokreta je spremna na micanje.
<p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PrivateZoneInitialState.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Početno stanje vaše Privatne Zone" + '"' + @" /><p />
Da biste pokrenuli flotu jednstavno kliknite na nju i onda kliknite na otkriveno područje. Tada  izaberite mogućnost " + '"' + @"Pokreni Flotu" + '"' + @". Sljedeći video će vam pokazati kako:
<p /></div>");
			Add("pt", "TravelContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
   Se quiseres [Travel] no universo só precisas de uma coisa: uma [Fleet] com unidades.
   <p />
   A imagem seguinte ilustra o estado inicial da private zone onde está disponivel uma fleet que se pode mover.
   <p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PrivateZoneInitialState.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Initial state of your Private Zone" + '"' + @" /><p />
   Para mover a unidade clica na unidade e depois clica numa zona descoberta e escolhe a opção " + '"' + @"Mover Armada" + '"' + @". O Video seguinte mostra como:
   <p /></div>");
			Add("de", "UniverseAttackContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    Um irgendetwas im [Universe] anzugreifen, muss du eine [Flotte] mit Einheiten haben.
    <p>
    Um einen anderen Spieler anzugreifen wähle einfach [Flotte] und klicke einfach über die [Flotte] 
    oder [Planet] des anderen Spielers.
    </p><p>
    Wenn du über die [Flotte] klickst, erscheint folgendes Menü:
    </p><p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/AttackFleet.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Attack a Fleet" + '"' + @" /></p><p>
    Nachdem du die Option 'Angriff' anklickst, wird deine [Flotte] sich in Bewegung setzen und die 
    [Flotte] des Feinds angreifen .
    </p><p>
    Wenn die Ziel [Flotte] in Bewegung ist, erscheint eine andere Option:
    </p><p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/AttackPursuit.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Flotte verfolgen" + '"' + @" /></p><p>
    Das bedeutet dass deine [Flotte] die Ziel [Flotte] verfolgt bis sie attackiert wird.
    </p><p>
    Wenn deine [Flotte] ein [Planet] attackiert, erscheinen die folgenden Optionen:
    <img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/Conquer2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Attack a Planet" + '"' + @" /></p><p>
    Diese Optionen bedeuten:
    </p><ul><li>Attackiere [Planet] und [Conquer]: Wenn es keine Verteidigung gibt dann hast du mit [Conquer] den [Planet] unverzüglich erobert. Andernfalls, ist eine [Battle] angefangen</li><li>Plündere [Planet]: Wenn es keine Verteidigungseinheiten gibt, stiehlst du die Ressourcen ohne [Battle]. Andernfalls, fängt eine [Battle] an und du kannst die Ressourcen nur stehlen wenn du gewinnst. In diesem Fall, Wird der [Planet] nicht erobert.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("en", "UniverseAttackContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    In order to attack something in the [Universe], you must have a [Fleet] with units inside.
    <p />
    To attack another player simply select your [Fleet] and click above the other player [Fleet] or [Planet].
    <p />
    If you click over a [Fleet], the following menu will appear:
    <p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/AttackFleet.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Attack a Fleet" + '"' + @" /><p />
    After you click in the option 'Attack', the [Fleet] will start moving and engage the enemy [Fleet].
    <p />
    If the target [Fleet] is moving, a diferent option will appear:
    <p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/AttackPursuit.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Pursuit a Fleet" + '"' + @" /><p />
    This means that your [Fleet] will pursuit the target [Fleet] until it is attacked.
    <p />
    When your [Fleet] attacks a [Planet], the following options will appear:
    <img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/Conquer2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Attack a Planet" + '"' + @" /><p />
    These options mean:
    <ul><li>Attack [Planet] and [Conquer]: If there is no defense you [Conquer] the [Planet] immediattly. Otherside, a [Battle] is started</li><li>Raid [Planet]: If there is no defense units, you steal the resources without a [Battle]. Otherside, a [Battle] is started and you only steal the resources if you win it. In this case, the [Planet] isn't conquered.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("hr", "UniverseAttackContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
Kako biste napali nešto u [Universe], morate imati [Fleet] koja sadrži jedinice.
<p />
Da napadnete drugog igrača jednostavno odaberite svoju Fleet] i kliknire iznad [Fleet] ili [Planet] drugog igrača
<p />
Ako kliknete preko [Fleet], sljedeći izbornik će se pojaviti:
<p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/AttackFleet.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Napadni Flotu" + '"' + @" /><p />
Makon što kliknete na opciju " + '"' + @"Napadni" + '"' + @", [Fleet] će se početi micati i napasti neprijateljsku [Fleet].
<p />
Kada vaša [Fleet] napadne [Planet], sljedeće mogućnosti će se pojaviti:
<img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/Conquer2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Napadni Planet" + '"' + @" /><p />
Ove mogućnosti znače:
<ul><li>Napadni [Planet] i [Conquer]: ako nema obrane vi [Conquer]  [Planet] odmah. Ako je ima [Battle] se započinje</li><li>Opljačkaj [Planet]: Ako nema obranbenih jednica, vi kradete reusrse bez [Battle].Ako ima [Battle] se započinje i vi možete ukrasti reusrse samo ako je dobijete. U ovom slučaju  [Planet] nije pokoren.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("pt", "UniverseAttackContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @">
    De modo a atacar alguma coisa no [Universe], tens de ter uma [Fleet] com unidades.
    <p />
    Para atacar outro jogador simplesmente selecciona a tua [Fleet] e clica sobre a [Fleet] ou [Planet] do jogador inimigo.
    <p />
    Se clicares sobre a [Fleet], a seguinte opção aparece:
    <p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/pt/AttackFleet.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Atacar Aramada" + '"' + @" /><p />
    Depois de clicares na opção 'Ataque', a [Fleet] vai iniciar o movimento e atacar a [Fleet] inimiga.
    <p />
    Se a [Fleet] alvo se estiver a mover, uma opção diferente aparece:
    <p /><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/pt/AttackPursuit.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Perseguir a Armada" + '"' + @" /><p />
    Isto significa que a [Fleet] vai perseguir a [Fleet] inimiga até que a possa atacar.
    <p />
    Quando uma [Fleet] ataca um [Planet], as opções seguintes aparecem:
    <img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/pt/Conquer2.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Attack a Planet" + '"' + @" /><p />
    Estas opções significam:
    <ul><li>Atacar [Planet] e [Conquer]: Se não existe defesa tu [Conquer] o [Planet] de imediato. Caso contrário uma [Battle] começa</li><li>Pilhar [Planet]: Se não existirem unidades de defesa, roubas os recursos ao dono do [Planet] sem [Battle]. Caso contrário uma [Battle] é começada e só roubas os recursos caso a venças. Neste caso, o [Planet] não é conquistado.</li></ul></div>");
			Add("de", "UnloadCargoInfo", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><p>Du kannst die Fracht einer Flotte nur dann entladen wenn diese Flotte in der Nähe eines Planeten ist, wie in dem folgenden Bild:</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/UnloadCargo1.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Flotte in der Nähe eines Planeten" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Flotte in der Nähe eines Planeten" + '"' + @" /><p>Um die Fracht einer Flotte abzuladen, gibt es zwei Möglichkeiten:</p><ul><li><p>Wenn die Flotte wie in dem Bild oben (in der Nähe eines Planeten das du besitzt), kannst du zum Flotten-Menü deines Planeten gehen und den Knopf anklicken " + '"' + @"Entlade fracht" + '"' + @":</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/UnloadCargo2.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"width: 450px;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" /></li><li><p>Alternativ dazu, kannst du auch die Bewegungs-Optionen deiner Flotte benutzen:</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/UnloadCargo3.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" /><p>Mit dieser Option wird die Flotte sich auf den Planeten zubewegen und automatisch die Fracht entladen.</p></li></ul></div>");
			Add("en", "UnloadCargoInfo", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><p>You can only unload cargo from a fleet if that fleet is near a planet, like in the following picture:</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/UnloadCargo1.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Fleet near a planet" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Fleet near a planet" + '"' + @" /><p>To unload the cargo of a fleet there are two possible ways:</p><ul><li><p>If the fleet is like in the above image (near a planet that you own), you can go the fleet menu of your planet and click in the button " + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @":</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/UnloadCargo2.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"width:450px;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" /></li><li><p>Alternatively, you can also use the movement options of your fleet:</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/UnloadCargo3.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" /><p>In this option the fleet will move towards the planet an it will unload all the cargo automatically.</p></li></ul></div>");
			Add("hr", "UnloadCargoInfo", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><p>Možete istovariti teret iz flote samo kada je ta flota blizu planetu, kao na sljedećoj slici :</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/UnloadCargo1.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Fleet near a planet" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Fleet near a planet" + '"' + @" /><p>Da istovarite teret flote postoje dva načina:</p><ul><li><p>Ako je slika kao na slici poviše (blizu planeta kojega vi posjedujete), možete ići u izbornik flote na vašem planetu i kliknuti na gumb " + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @":</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/UnloadCargo2.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"width:450px;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" /></li><li><p>Alternativno, možete se koristiti mogućnosti pokreta vaše flote:</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/UnloadCargo3.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" /><p>U ovoj mogućnosti flota će krenuti prema planetu i isotvariti će teret automatski.</p></li></ul></div>");
			Add("pt", "UnloadCargoInfo", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><p>Só podes descarrega a carga de uma armada se a armada estiver ao lado de um planeta teu (tal como podes ver na figura seguinte):</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/UnloadCargo1.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Fleet near a planet" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Fleet near a planet" + '"' + @" /><p>Para descarregar a carga existem duas maneiras possiveis:</p><ul><li><p>Se a armada estiver como na imagem acima (próxima de um aplaneta teu), vais ao menu fleet desse planet e clicas no botão " + '"' + @"Descarregar Carga" + '"' + @". </p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/pt/UnloadCargo2.png" + '"' + @" style=" + '"' + @"width:450px;" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" /></li><li><p>Em alternativa podes usar o menu de movimento da tua fleet, tal como na imagem seguinte:</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/pt/UnloadCargo3.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Unload Cargo" + '"' + @" /><p>Nesta opção, a fleet vai-se mover para o teu planet e quando lá chegar irá descarregar automaticamente os recursos.</p></li></ul></div>");
			Add("de", "WormHoleContent", @"<div class=" + '"' + @"content" + '"' + @"><div style=" + '"' + @"float: right;" + '"' + @"><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/WormHole.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Worm Hole" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Worm Hole" + '"' + @" /></div><p>Das [WormHole] wird benutzt um eine [Fleet] unverzüglich von einem Punkt zum anderen im [Universe] zu transportieren.</p><p>In jeder [PrivateZone] gibt es ein [WormHole] das dich mit dem Rest des [Universe] verbindet. Da es versteckt ist, musst du danach suchen.
 Das [WormHole] ist auch privat. Das bedeutet dass du der einzige bist der es benutzen kann. Unten ist ein Bild einer unerforschten [PrivateZone] mit dem [WormHole].</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/PrivateWormHole.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Private Worm Hole" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Private Worm Hole" + '"' + @" /><p> Um ein neues Wurmloch zu erforschen musst du es nur benutzen. Dafür, musst du auf eine [Fleet] klicken und dann auf das[WormHole]. 
    Wenn du dies tust, erscheint das folgende Popup-Menü:</p><img src=" + '"' + @"/Resources/Images/en/WormHole.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Worm Hole Popup" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Worm Hole Popup" + '"' + @" /><p>Wenn du Transport anklickst, erscheint ein Fenster mit allen verfügbaren [WormHoles].</p><p>Diese Fenster hat 2 Tabs:
    </p><ul><li>Universe [WormHoles] - Alle öffentlichen [WormHoles] die du gefunden hast</li><li>Alliance [WormHoles] - Alle [WormHoles] deiner Allianz oder die du gebaut hast (Diese [WormHoles] können nur von den [Bugs] gebaut werden. Mehr Information siehe unten).</li></ul><h1>[Bugs] Wormhole</h1><p>Diese spezielle Art von [WormHole] ist die ultimative Waffe der [Bugs]. Dieses [WormHole] kann nur von dir benutzt werden , und auf höheren Entwicklungsebenen, von den Mitgliedern deiner Allianz.</p><p>
 Jedes gebaut [WormHole] hat ein Level. Das Level wird angegeben durch die Summe der Level deines [WormHoleCreator]. Beispiel: Wenn du 3 [WormHoleCreator] Level 1 und 1 [WormHoleCreator] Level 2 hast,
 dann wird dein [WormHole] Level 5 sein.
    </p><h1>States</h1>
