			Add("se", "DarkHumans", @"Renegades");
			Add("de", "DarkHumansLore", @"<p>Die Aufteilung der Rebellfraktionen der Utopians und die Formation der Renegades war ein abrupter, aber erwarteter Ausgang. Nach ihrer Flucht zu einem anderen System, indem sie die gestohlene Wurmloch Technologie benutzten, wollten die Renegades ein Klon des Projekt Utopia machen, aber mit den knappen Ressourcen die ihnen anfänglich zur Verfügung standen, kamen die Renegades auf die Idee mechanische Implantate zu benutzen um ihre Lebensdauer zu erhöhen. Dies gab ihnen zusätzliche Kraft und Resistenz, was sie zu einem bösartigen Gegner machte. Sie lebten von der Piraterie und organisiertem Handel zwischen ihren Gruppen. Letzendlich, waren sie dann in der Lage aus den Schatten zu kommen und den Utopians Front zu machen.</p><p>Die Allianz mit dem neu gefundenen Levyr und ihren gemeinsamen Zielen machten sie sehr mächtig und eine Bedrohung für die Utopians. Das zweite Zeitalter von Orion kann das Zeitalter der Renegades sein!</p><p>Ihre einzigartigen Ressourcen sind <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/GoldSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Gold" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Gold" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/TitaniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Titanium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Titanium" + '"' + @" /> and <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/UraniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Uranium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Uranium" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("en", "DarkHumansLore", @"<p>The splitting of the rebel factions of the Utopians and the formation of the Renegades was an abrupt but expected outcome. After their escape to another system using the stolen wormhole technology, the Renegades felt they should do a clone of Project Utopia, but with the scarce resources they had in the beginning, the Renegades came up with the idea of using mechanical implants to further their lifespan. This also gave them more strength and resistance which made them a vicious enemy. They lived off space piracy and organized trade between their groups. Then, they finally were able to move out of the shadows and impose themselves in sight of the Utopians.</p><p>The alliance with the newly found Levyr and their joint objectives made them powerful and a threat to the Utopians. The Second Age of Orion can be the Age of the Renegades!</p><p>Their unique resources are <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/GoldSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Gold" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Gold" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/TitaniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Titanium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Titanium" + '"' + @" /> and <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/UraniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Uranium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Uranium" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("fr", "DarkHumansLore", @"<p>La séparation de la facion rebelle des [LightHumans] et la formation des [DarkHumans] fût rapide mais prévisible. Suite à leur fuite vers un autre système à l'aide de la technologie de création de trous stellaire volée, les [DarkHumans] ont décidés de clôner le projet " + '"' + @"Utupia" + '"' + @". Ayant peu de ressources au départ, les [DarkHumans] ont eu l'idée d'utiliser des implants mécaniques pour allonger leur durée de vie. Cela leur donna aussi une force et résistance hors du commun, fesant d'eux un adversaire redoutable. La plupart ont d'abord vécu à l'aoide de pilage et en organisant des échanges entre groupes. Ensuite, ils sont devenus assez puissant pour sortir de l'ombre et révéler leur vrai visage à l'univers en s'imposant aux [LightHumans].</p><p>Leur nouvelle alliance avec les [Bugs] et lleurs objectifs commun les rendent enocre plus puissantet en fait une vrai menace pour les [LightHumans]. TLa deixème âge 'Orions pourrait bien être elle des [DarkHumans]! The Second Age of Orion can be the Age of the Renegades!</p><p>Leurs ressources uniques sont <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/GoldSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Gold" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Gold" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/TitaniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Titanium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Titanium" + '"' + @" /> and <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/UraniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Uranium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Uranium" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("hr", "DarkHumansLore", @"<p> Razdvajanje pubunjeničke fakcije od Utopiansa i formiranje Renegadesa je žestok ali očekivan ishod. Nakon njihovoga bijega u drugi sustav služeći se ukradenom tehnologijom crvotočina, Renegades su osjetili da bi mogli napraviti kopiju projekta Utopia, ali sa nedovljnim resursima koje su imali u početku, Renagades su došli na ideju da upotrijebe mehaničke implante da produže svoj životni vijek. Ovo im je također dalo više snage i otpornosti koja je od njih napravila opakog neprijatelja. Živjeli su od svemirskog piratstva i organizirane trgovine između njihovih grupa. Kasnije su napokon uspjeli da iziđu iz sjene i otkriju se Utopiansima. </p><p> Savez sa novopronađenim Levyrima i njihov zajednički cilj učinio ih je moćnima i prijetnjom Utopiansima.
Drugo doba Oriona može biti doba Renegadesa!</p><p>Njihovu jedinstveni resursi su  <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/GoldSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Gold" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Gold" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/TitaniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Titanium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Titanium" + '"' + @" /> and <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/UraniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Uranium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Uranium" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("pt", "DarkHumansLore", @"<p>A divisão das facções rebeldes dos Utopianos e a formação dos Renegados era um final esperado. Após escaparem para outro sistema usando a tecnologia de wormhole roubada, os Renegados sentiram que deviam clonar o projecto Utopia. Mas, com os fracos recursos que eles tinham de início, os Renegados tiverama ideia de usar implantes mecânicos para aumentar a sua longevidade. Isto deu-lhes mais força e resistência o que os tornou um inimigo poderoso. Viviam de pirataria espacial e de trocas comerciais entre os seus diversos grupos. Então, eles foram finalmente capazes de sair das sombras e fazer frente aos Utopianos.</p><p>A aliança com os Levyr e os seus objectivos comuns tornaram-os poderosos e uma ameaça para os Utopianos. A segunda era de Orion pode muito bem ser a Era dos Renegados!</p><p>Os seus recursos únicos são <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/GoldSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Gold" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Gold" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/TitaniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Titanium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Titanium" + '"' + @" /> e <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/UraniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Uranium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Uranium" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("se", "DarkHumansLore", @"<p>
När rebellerna splittrades från Utopians och  Renegades skapades så var det en abrupt men väntad konsekvens. Efter deras flykt till ett annat system genom att använda stulen maskhåls-teknologi kände Renegades att de borde göra en klon av Projekt Utopia men med de små resurser de hade i början så kom Renegades på idén att använda mekaniska implantat för att förlänga sina liv. Det gav dem även mer styrka och motståndskraft vilket gjorde dem till en farlig fiende. De levde på piratverksamhet och organiserad handel mellan deras grupper. Tillslut kunde flytta ut ur skuggorna och hävda sig inför Utopians.
</p><p>
Alliansen med de nyfunna Levyr och deras gemensamma mål gjorde dem kraftfulla och ett hot mod Utopians. Orions Andra Tidsållder kan bli Renegades tidsålder.
</p><p>
Deras unika resurser är <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/GoldSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Guld" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Guld" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/TitaniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Titan" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Titan" + '"' + @" /> och <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/UraniumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Uran" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Uran" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("de", "DarkMercsFleetDescription", @"Dies sind die gefürchtesten Einheiten in der ganzen Merc Flotte. Sie haben alle möglichen Einheiten zu ihrer Verfügung, inklusive der zerstörerischen <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Titan.aspx" + '"' + @">Titan</a>, eine mächtige, schwere Einheit. Sei gewarnt : sie sind grösser in der Anzahl und Feuerkraft. Diese Flotten sieht man nur in Level 10 Zonen.");
			Add("en", "DarkMercsFleetDescription", @"These are the most Fierced units in the Mercs all Fleet. They have all kinds of units at their disposal including the destructive <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Titan.aspx" + '"' + @">Titan</a>, a powerful heavy unit. Be aware: their are great both in numbers and fire power. This fleets are only seen in level 10 areas.");
			Add("hr", "DarkMercsFleetDescription", @"Ovo su najžešće jedinice u svoj  Mercs floti. Oni imaju sve vrste jedinica na raspolaganju uključujući destruktivnog <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Titan.aspx" + '"' + @">Titana</a>, moćnu tešku jedinicu. Pazite se: oni su jaki i brojčano i sa vatrenom moći. Njihove flote su samo viđene u lv 10 područjima.");
			Add("it", "DarkMercsFleetDescription", @"Queste sono le armate più temute delle flotte Mercs. Hanno tutti i tipi di unità a loro disposizione compreso il <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Titan.aspx" + '"' + @">Titan</a>, una potente unità pesante. Fai attenzione: sono numerosi e potenti. Queste flotte son state viste solo nelle aree di livello 10.");
			Add("pt", "DarkMercsFleetDescription", @"Estas são as mais temidas armadas em toda a frota dos Mercs. Elas possuem todos os tipos de unidades incuindo as destrutivas <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/pt/Unit/Titan.aspx" + '"' + @">Titã</a>, uma poderosa unidade de grande porte. Tem cuidado: eles são poderosos tanto em numbers como em poder de fogo. Estas armadas são vistas apenas em zonas de nível 10.");
			Add("se", "DarkMercsFleetDescription", @"Dessa är de mest fruktade enheterna Mercs Flottor. De har alla typer av enheter till dess förfogande inclusive den destruktiva enheten <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Titan.aspx" + '"' + @">Titan</a>, en kraftfull tung enhet. Var försiktig: de är både stora i antal och i eldkraft. Den här enheten syns endast i områden i nivå 10.");
			Add("de", "LightHumans", @"Utopians");
			Add("en", "LightHumans", @"Utopians");
			Add("es", "LightHumans", @"Utopianos");
			Add("fr", "LightHumans", @"Utopians");
			Add("hr", "LightHumans", @"Utopians");
			Add("pt", "LightHumans", @"Utopianos");
			Add("se", "LightHumans", @"Utopians");
			Add("de", "LightHumansDetails", @"Einheiten:");
			Add("en", "LightHumansDetails", @"Units:");
			Add("es", "LightHumansDetails", @"Unidades:");
			Add("fr", "LightHumansDetails", @"Unités:");
			Add("hr", "LightHumansDetails", @"Jedinice:");
			Add("pt", "LightHumansDetails", @"Unidades:");
			Add("se", "LightHumansDetails", @"Enheter:");
			Add("de", "LightHumansLore", @"<p>Nach der Enthüllung des Projekt Utopia und die Pläne die Lebensdauer eines normalen Menschen durch die Wissenschaft der Medizin zu steigern, änderten die Menschen ihre Namen zu Utopians. " + '"' + @"Utopia" + '"' + @" würde sie in die LAge versetzen sich im Universum auszubreiten, und weitere Planet zu bevölkern. Dennoch der Konflikt mit den neugeformten Renegades und der Diebstahl der Wurmloch-Technologie Entwürfe waren ein Rückschlag in den Plänen der Utopians. Das Aufsteigen der Levyr und ihre Allianz mit den Renegades waren Bedrohungen die die Utopians nicht länger ignorieren konnten um ihres Überlebens willen.</p><p>Das zweite Zeitalter von Orion auf der Utopian Seite markiert einen totale Änderung ihrer Ziele: nicht länger sind sie die dominante Kraft im Universum, aber sie wurden auch noch zur gejagten Fraktion deren Kriegsbeute nach der Niederlage, mehr als genug ist um zwischen die Allianz die sie gejagt hat, aufzuteilen.</p><p>Ihre einzigartigen Ressourcen sind <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/EnergySmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Energy" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Energy" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/SeriumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" /> and <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/MithrilSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("en", "LightHumansLore", @"<p>After the unveiling of Project Utopia and the plans to enhance the lifetime of a normal human via medical science, the humans changed their name to Utopians. " + '"' + @"Utopia" + '"' + @" would enable them to spread over the universe, colonize and populate more planets. Still the conflict with the newly formed Renegades and the stealing of the wormhole technology blueprints were a setback in the plans of the Utopians. Also, the rising up of the Levyr and their alliance with the Renegades were threats that the Utopians could not ignore any longer for the sake of their survival.</p><p>The Second Age of Orion on the Utopian side marks a total shift in their objectives: no longer are they the dominant force on the universe but also they have become the hunted faction whose spoils after defeat are more than enough to share between the alliance that was hunting them.</p><p>Their unique resources are <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/EnergySmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Energy" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Energy" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/SeriumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" /> and <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/MithrilSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("fr", "LightHumansLore", @"<p>Suite à l'ambitieux ambitieux projet Utopia et leurs plans d'augmenter dratiquement la longévité d'un humain normal grâce à la science médical, les humains ont changés leur nom pour [LightHumans]. Leur " + '"' + @"Utopie" + '"' + @"  leur aurait permis de se répandre à travers l'univers et coloniser d'autres planètes. Le conflit engendrée avec l'apparition des [DarkHumans] et leur vol de la technologie de fabrication de trou stellaire a été quelque peu nuisible pour les [LightHumans]. De plus, l'inquiétante progression des [Bugs] sur l'univers et leur alliance  avec les [DarkHumans] fût une menace pour les [LightHumans] qu'il ne pouvaient ignorer, question de survie.</p><p>L'entrée dans le deuxième âge d'Orions belt marque un changement drastique des objectifs des Utopiens. Ils ne sont plus la force dominante sur l'univers, ils sont même la proie dont les trésors semble suffisant pour satisfaire leurs adversaires.</p><p>Leurs ressources uniques sont <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/EnergySmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Energy" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Energy" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/SeriumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" /> and <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/MithrilSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("hr", "LightHumansLore", @"<p> Nakon razotkrivanja Projekta Utopia i planova da se produži život normalnog čovjeka kroz medicinsku znanost ljudi su promijenili svoje imu u Utopians. " + '"' + @"Utopia" + '"' + @" bi im omogućila da se prošire svemirom, koloniziraju i napuče više planeta. Ipak sukob s novoformiranim Renegadesima i kranje nacrat tehnologije o crvotočinama je bila prepreka u planovima Utopiansa. Također uspon Levyra i njihovo savezništvo sa Renegadesima je bila prijetnja koju Utopiansi nisu mogli više ignorirati ukoliko su mislili osigurati vlastito preživljavanje.</p><p> Drugo Doba Oriona na strani Utopiansa označava potpuni zaokret u njihovim ciljevima: oni više nisu dominantna sila u svemiru već su postali progonjena fakcija čiji je ratni plijen nakon poraza i više nego dovoljan da ga podijele saveznici koji su ih lovili.</p><p>Njihovi jedinstveni reusrsi su:
<img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/EnergySmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Energy" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Energy" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/SeriumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" /> and <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/MithrilSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("pt", "LightHumansLore", @"<p>Após o desvendar do projecto Utopia e os planos para aumentar o tempo de vida normal de um ser humano através de ciência médica, os humanos mudaram os seus nomes para Utopianos. " + '"' + @"Utopia" + '"' + @" iria permitir-lhes espalhar por todo o universo, colonizar e popular mais planetas. Contudo, o conflito com a recente formada facção de Renegados e o roubo dos planos para a nova tecnologia de wormhole foi um grande recuo nos planos dos Utopianos. O erguer dos Levyr e a sua aliança com os Renegados foram ameaças que os Utopianos não podia ignorar. A sua sobrevivência estava em risco.</p><p>A segunda era de Orion, para os Utopianos, marca uma mudança nos seus planos: não só não são a força dominante no universo como também se tornaram uma facção caçada cujos despojos após a derrota são mais que suficientes para partilhar entre a aliança que os caça.</p><p>Os seus recursos únicos são <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/EnergySmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Energy" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Energy" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/SeriumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" /> e o <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/MithrilSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
			Add("se", "LightHumansLore", @"<p>
Efter starten av Projekt Utopia och planerna på att förlänga livstiden hos en vanlig männsika med hjälp av vetenskap ändrade människorna sina namn till Utopians. Utopia skulle hjälpa dem att sprida sig över universum, att kolonialisera och befolka fler planeter. Fortfarande var konflikten med de nyformade Renegades och stölden av ritningarna till maskhålsteknologin ett bakslag för Utopians planer. Dessutom var uppvaknandet av Levyr och deras allians med Renegades hot som Utopians in kunder ignorera längre om de skulle överleva.
</p><p>
Orions Andra Ålder innebar för Utopians ett markant skifte i deras planer: ej längre är de den dominanta kraften i Universum och der har också blivit den jagade rasen vars byte vid nederlag är mer än väl att dela mellan alliansen som jagade dem.
</p><p>
Deras unika resurser är  <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/EnergySmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Energi" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Energi" + '"' + @" />, <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/SeriumSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Serium" + '"' + @" /> och <img src=" + '"' + @"http://resources.orionsbelt.eu/Images/Common/Resources/MithrilSmall.png" + '"' + @" alt=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" title=" + '"' + @"Mithril" + '"' + @" />.</p>");
