			Add("de", "RogueMercsFleetDescription", @"Diese Flotten patrouillieren die Level 5 Zone. Sind sind ein Upgrade der Sentry Mercs Flotte und deshalb besitzen sie eine neue Art von Einheit, eine Medium Einheit: <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Scourge.aspx" + '"' + @">Scourge</a>.");
			Add("en", "RogueMercsFleetDescription", @"This fleets patrol the level 5 area. Their are an upgrade to the Sentry Mercs fleet and, because of that, they have available a new kind of unit, a medium unit: <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Scourge.aspx" + '"' + @">Scourge</a>.");
			Add("hr", "RogueMercsFleetDescription", @"Ove flote patroliraju kroz nivo 5 područje. Oni su poboljšanje  Sentry Mercs flota i zbog toga imaju dostupnu novu jedinicu (srednju): <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Scourge.aspx" + '"' + @">Biča</a>.");
			Add("it", "RogueMercsFleetDescription", @"Queste flotte pattugliano l'area di livello 5. Sono un'evoluzione delle flotte dei Sentry Mercs e, per questo motivo, hanno a disposizione un nuovo tipo di unità media: lo <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Scourge.aspx" + '"' + @">Scourge</a>.");
			Add("pt", "RogueMercsFleetDescription", @"Estas armadas patrulham a zona de nível 5. Elas são uma evolução dos Sentry Mercs e, devido a isso, possuem um novo tipo de unidade, uma unidade de médio Porte: O <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/pt/Unit/Scourge.aspx" + '"' + @">Flagelo</a>.");
			Add("se", "RogueMercsFleetDescription", @"Den här flottan patrullerar nivå 5. De är en uppgradering av Sentry Mercs flotta och de har, på grund av detta, en ny typ av enhet tillgänglig, En mellanenhet: <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Scourge.aspx" + '"' + @">Scourge</a>.");
			Add("de", "SentryMercsFleetDescription", @"Weniger opulent als die Mercs Flotte, sind die Seentry Mercs ausgerüstet mit zwei Arten von Einheiten: the <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Sentry.aspx" + '"' + @">Sentrys</a> und die erbitterten <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Reaper.aspx" + '"' + @">Reapers</a>. Ihr Jagdrevier ist die gesamte level 3 Zone.");
			Add("en", "SentryMercsFleetDescription", @"A little less abundant than the Mercs Fleet, the Seentry Mercs are equiped with two kinds of units: the <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Sentry.aspx" + '"' + @">Sentrys</a> and the fierced <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Reaper.aspx" + '"' + @">Reapers</a>. Their hunt ground are all the level 3 area.");
			Add("hr", "SentryMercsFleetDescription", @"Malo manje izdašne nego Mercs Flote, Seentry Mercs su opremljene sa dvije vrste jedinica:  
 <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Sentry.aspx" + '"' + @">Stražari</a> and the fierced <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Reaper.aspx" + '"' + @">Žetalice</a>. Njihovo lovušte je područje nivoa 3.");
			Add("pt", "SentryMercsFleetDescription", @"Um pouco menos abundantes que as armadas de Mercs, os Sentry Mercs estão equipados com 2 tipos de unidades: as <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/pt/Unit/Sentry.aspx" + '"' + @">Sentry</a> e as temidas <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/pt/Unit/Reaper.aspx" + '"' + @">Reaper</a>. O seu terreno de caça são zonas de nível 3.");
			Add("se", "SentryMercsFleetDescription", @"Finn i lite mindre antal än Mercs Flottor, Sentry Mercs är utrustade med två typer av enheter: <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Sentry.aspx" + '"' + @">Sentrys</a> och den fruktade <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/Reaper.aspx" + '"' + @">Reaper</a>. Deras jaktmarker är hela området i nivå 3.");
			Add("de", "SilverBeardFleetDescription", @"Dies ist die zweitmächtigste Flotte in der ganzen Merc Armee. Geführt von Silber Bart selbst, wird es kommandiert von der zweitmächtigsten Einheit in der Flotte. Ihr Aufenthaltsort ist unbekannt aber Berichte sagen dass diese einzigartige Flotte ihre Angriffe zwischen Level 7 und Level 10 Zonen macht. Sei sehr vorsichtig. Ihre Anzahl und Feuerkraft sind enorm und die <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/SilverBeard.aspx" + '"' + @">Silver Beard's</a> Einheit ist einer der mächtigsten im Universum.");
			Add("en", "SilverBeardFleetDescription", @"This is the second most powerfull fleet in all the Merc army. Lead by Silver Beard himself, it is command by the second most powerfull unit in the fleet. It's location is unknown by reports say that this unique fleet makes its raids in between level 7 and level 10 areas. Be very careful. Their numbers and fire power are huge and
   <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/SilverBeard.aspx" + '"' + @">Silver Beard's</a> unit is the  Mercs fleet.");
			Add("hr", "SilverBeardFleetDescription", @"Ovo je druga najmoćnija flota u čitavoj Mercs vojsci. Vođena od Srebrene Brade osobno, koji zapovijeda drugim najmoćnijim brodom u floti. Njihova lokacija je nepoznata ali izvještaji govore da ova jedinstvena flota pljačka izmežu područja nivoa 7 i 10. Budite jako oprezni. Njihovi brojevi i vatrena moć su ogromni i <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/SilverBeard.aspx" + '"' + @">Srebrene Brada</a> jedinica je Mercs flota.");
			Add("pt", "SilverBeardFleetDescription", @"É a segunda armada mais poderosa na armada Merc. Liderada pelo Barba de Prata, esta armada é comandada pela segunda mais poderosa unidade em toda a armada de Mercs. A sua localização é desconhecida mas relatos dizem que esta armada costuma fazer os seus saques entre zonas de nível 7 e nível 10. O seu número e poder de fogo são enromes e
   a <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/pt/Unit/SilverBeard.aspx" + '"' + @">unidade comandada pelo Barba de Prata</a> é a uma das mais poderosas no universo.");
			Add("se", "SilverBeardFleetDescription", @"Det här är den näst kraftfullaste flottan i Merc's armé. Ledda av Silverskägg själv, styrs den av den mest kraftulla enheten i flottan. Dess plats är okänd men rapperter säger att denna unika flotta gör sina röder mellan nivå 7 och 10. Var väldigt försiktig. Dess antal och eldkraft är ofantliga och <a href=" + '"' + @"http://manual.orionsbelt.eu/en/Unit/SilverBeard.aspx" + '"' + @">Silverskäggs</a> enhet är den mest kraftfulla i Universum.");
			Add("de", "TechMercsFleetDescription", @"Diese Flotten sind ähnlich zu den Rogue Mercs Flotten. Der einzige Unterschied ist dass sie in der Anzahl grösser sind. Diese Flotten erscheinen in Level 7 Zonen.");
			Add("en", "TechMercsFleetDescription", @"These fleets are very similar to the Rogue Mercs Fleets. The only diference is that they are only greater in numbers. These fleets appear in the level 7 areas.");
			Add("hr", "TechMercsFleetDescription", @"Ove flote su jako slične flotama  Rogue Mercs-a. Jedina razlika je da oni imaju više brodova. Pojavljuju se u nivo 7 područjima.");
			Add("it", "TechMercsFleetDescription", @"Queste flotte sono molto simili alle flotte dei Rogue Mercs. L'unica differenza è che sono più numerose. Queste flotte appaiono nelle aree di livello 7.");
			Add("pt", "TechMercsFleetDescription", @"Estas armadas são muito similares às armadas Rogue Mercs. A única diferença é que são maiores em termos de número. Estas fleets aparecem em zonas de nível 7.");
			Add("se", "TechMercsFleetDescription", @"De här flottorna är väldigt lika Rouge Mercs flottor. Den enda skillnaden är att de är ännu fler i antal. Dessa flottor återfinns i områden i nivå 7.");
